===Etymology===
The kanji are {{juku}}; borrowed from {{bor|ja|zh|彼}} + {{l|zh|方}}.
{{rfe|ja|From where comes the "chira" suffix in {{ja-r|何方|どちら}}, {{ja-r|此方|こちら}}, and {{ja-r|彼方|あちら}}; & the "nata" suffix in {{ja-r|何方|どなた}}, {{ja-r|此方|こなた}}, and {{ja-r|彼方|かなた}}?}}

